<section class="section section--tint sr-prose">
  <div class="container--narrow">
    <h2 class="sr-prose__heading">Free Shipping Policy</h2>
    <p>We offer free shipping to all/any product orders over $500.00 for all U.S States except Hawaii, Alaska and Puerto Rico. The shipping price for orders above $500.00 will be automatically adjusted at checkout to $0.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sr-prose__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .sr-prose p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .sr-prose p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
